annotations.title: 10 Easy Cocktails To Make At Home

textContent:
3 blackberries
.75oz lemon
.75oz simple syrup
2oz gin

Muddle 3 blackberries into rocks glass
Whip shake other ingredients with crushed ice. 
Pour on top of blackberries and top with crushed ice. 
Garnish with blackberry
